- <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ideal_(order_theory)>
- <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cofinal_(mathematics)>
- <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rasiowa%E2%80%93Sikorski_lemma>

